      • setPrefilledChallenge

        public AuthenticationParam.AuthenticationParamBuilder setPrefilledChallenge(java.lang.String challenge)
        If you previously got the challenge, call this method to tell us. Note that you do not have to call setIWrapGetChallengeStr(IWrapGetChallengeStr) if you pass a valid challenge via this method.
        参数:
        challenge - the pre-got challenge
        返回:
        the param model itself

      • setIWrapGetChallengeStr

        public AuthenticationParam.AuthenticationParamBuilder setIWrapGetChallengeStr(IWrapGetChallengeStr IWrapGetChallengeStr)
        Set the get challenge wrapper so that we can try to fetch the challenge via network. Note that the wrapper would be useless if you pass a valid challenge by calling setPrefilledChallenge(String)
        参数:
        IWrapGetChallengeStr - The network wrapper used to fetch challenge from network.
        返回:
        the param model itself

      • setIWrapUploadSignature

        public AuthenticationParam.AuthenticationParamBuilder setIWrapUploadSignature(IWrapUploadSignature IWrapUploadSignature)
        Set the get upload signature wrapper so that we can try to upload the final result via network. Instead of returning error, we will fill the final result to you in the end.
        参数:
        IWrapUploadSignature - The network wrapper used to upload the final result.
        返回:
        the param model itself

      • setSoterFingerprintStateCallback

        public AuthenticationParam.AuthenticationParamBuilder setSoterFingerprintStateCallback(SoterFingerprintStateCallback soterFingerprintStateCallback)
        The fingerprint status callback so that you can acknowledge the authentication status. Note that it is only the fingerprint authentication callback, do not use it as the process result, just used for updating UI.
        参数:
        soterFingerprintStateCallback - The fingerprint callback
        返回:
        the param model itself
